  "day": "6",
  "heading": "Trek from Dison to Dawar. Drive to Srinagar",
  "sub_heading": "Trek Distance: 4.6 km | Trek Duration: 3 hours\nDrive Distance: 141 km | Drive Duration: 6-7 hours | Altitude loss: 10,340 ft to 5,220 ft",
  "details": "Please note: The distance between campsites may vary by 100 meters depending on weather conditions and your route. The altitude may also vary by 100 feet for similar reasons."
}

{
  "day": "7",
  "heading": "Buffer Day",
  "sub_heading": "All your travel plans include a buffer day to accommodate bad weather on the trek/political instability. This depends entirely on the circumstances of the trek and the situation in Kashmir. The buffer day is mandatory to keep in your itinerary.",
  "details": "If the buffer day is used,  you have to pay us Rs 1,800 per day +5% GST. The money will be collected by the Trek Leader only if we use the buffer day."
}
